README for Image Uploader
This document is a work in progress.

Image Uploader is designed as an easy, fast way of uploading an image for use on the web. It runs on Windows, OS X, and Linux. 

License:
See the file 'COPYING'

Installation instructions:
Please read 'INSTALL' file.

Features: 

* Auto-resizing of the image into a web-publishable version and thumbnaili
* User-definable sizes 
* FTP support (sFTP is planned)
* Cross-platform (Windows/OS X/Linux/Anything that wxruby rmagick run on)
* Other stuff
